stylometry: Desicion trees are important beacuse they give us a way to see what the possible options are before we choose which desicion is best. This is used to find the optimum course of action in situations having several possible choices. A desicion tree can be used to determine whether a company should start a new product or not. This will allow the company the chance to see if the product will make money or not. They could start by using it in a small marekt first and see if they want to make it national or even global. a desicion tree will help by showing if it is feasible to enter each of the markets.
